    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a slump though. it feels permanent. like the well is actually dry. if the thing that made me 'me' is gone, then what's actually left? just a shell. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen that I know isn't coming. it's exhausting just existing when there's nothing inside to drive it.",
